## Visual

A dark navy and gold illuminated-manuscript style poster uses a tall modular layout with framed panels, serif capitals, and glowing cyan/gold diagram accents. The central narrative moves from an ordered state space to a graph to a marked target, flanked by before/after lattice diagrams showing amplitude concentrating around a selected state. Symbolic imagery includes cover graphs, upper ideals, target halos, orbital/star maps, geometric seals, and a bottom process chain from “mark” to “manifestation.”
